### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Send notification (Idempotency-Key required)
POST http://localhost:8080/notifications
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: notif-20260317-001

{
  "title": "System Maintenance",
  "message": "Scheduled maintenance starts at 11 PM.",
  "target_users": ["user-1", "user-2", "user-3"],
  "priority": "normal"
}
